# 1- Install this extension: 
    # https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/gnome-shell-integration/gphhapmejobijbbhgpjhcjognlahblep

# 2- open termainal and execute the following command:
     sudo apt install chrome-gnome-shell

# 4- after that open this link: https://extensions.gnome.org/extension/779/clipboard-indicator/
# 5- and toggle on the Clipboard Indicator

# if there's error try the following:
# - restart the browser
# - restarting your machine
# - retry on other browsers (eg. chrome, edge, firefox, & brave)
